{"tid":1004549,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【80年代無綫索花旦】當年係劉德華女友 陳敏兒揀廖啟智因為……","createTime":"2019-02-01T13:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T01:18:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"270a0114c152caca781812c88a95d18c55417362","tid":1004549,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T13:46:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190201/2_651957_0/-80年代無綫索花旦-當年係劉德華女友-陳敏兒揀廖啟智因為-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190201%2F2_651957_0%2F-80%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E7%B4%A2%E8%8A%B1%E6%97%A6-%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E4%BF%82%E5%8A%89%E5%BE%B7%E8%8F%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B-%E9%99%B3%E6%95%8F%E5%85%92%E6%8F%80%E5%BB%96%E5%95%9F%E6%99%BA%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA-&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsrAecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=c7c6ac3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190201%2F2_651957_0%2F-80%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E7%B4%A2%E8%8A%B1%E6%97%A6-%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E4%BF%82%E5%8A%89%E5%BE%B7%E8%8F%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B-%E9%99%B3%E6%95%8F%E5%85%92%E6%8F%80%E5%BB%96%E5%95%9F%E6%99%BA%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA-&h=d3b25525\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190201/2_651957_0/-80年代無綫索花旦-當年係劉德華女友-陳敏兒揀廖啟智因為-</a><br />\n<br />\n【80年代無綫索花旦】當年係劉德華女友 陳敏兒揀廖啟智因為&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/video/20190129/480pix/1548768865_e1d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fvideo%2F20190129%2F480pix%2F1548768865_e1d2.jpg&h=7cbb5e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廖啟智和陳敏兒是79年訓練班同學，開課3個月就開始拍拖。<br />\n<br />\n由於陳敏兒外形標緻，發展順利，好快就擔正女主角，更在劉德華成名作《獵鷹》，跟他飾演情侶，外形襯絕。<br />\n<br />\n之後她一直受大台力捧，除了做《體育世界》及其他大騷主持，更不斷有劇拍，差不多部部都擔正。<br />\n<br />\n拍拖多年，她已經變成上位花旦，但當時智叔仍然是配角，發展有差距，令他好大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n事業距離，加上智叔以前不相信一紙婚書，所以一直沒計劃結婚。<br />\n<br />\n但陳敏兒很想有自己的家庭，而且覺得跟智叔有說不完的話題，他向來是她的最佳聽眾，一直希望跟他廝守一生。<br />\n<br />\n所以拍拖第9年，她終於忍不住，喊住跟智叔講想結婚，嚇到智叔即刻話：「好！好！好！」<br />\n<br />\n不過因為不想有壓力，結婚都沒大搞，只是註冊，之後與家人食飯，直到結婚20周年，於07年才再入教堂行禮。<br />\n<br />\n敏兒相信婚姻是「路遙知馬力」，更指智叔好愛她，對她好包容，過去在相處上的跌跌碰碰、眼淚和傷害，成為肥料，滋養他們的婚姻；沒過往的經歷，亦不會有現在的成果。<br />\n<br />\n立即下載《壹週刊》Apps，隨時隨地睇盡時政專題、深度偵查、娛樂熱話！<br />\n<br />\n按此連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/next28app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fnext28app&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsrAecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=d41d903c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/next28app</a> <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞:【結婚31年〡喪子13年】曾怪廖啟智喪子後軟弱 陳敏兒：我覺得佢冇用睇唔起佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2RlgeT7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RlgeT7&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsrAecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=069a4a90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2RlgeT7</a>  <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【結婚31年〡喪子13年】曾怪廖啟智喪子後軟弱 陳敏兒：我覺得佢冇用睇唔起佢<br />\n<br />\n更多 壹週刊 文章<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【結婚31年〡喪子13年】曾怪廖啟智喪子後軟弱 陳敏兒：我覺得佢冇用睇唔起佢"},{"pid":"934f8e582d0933a099400732b9b7e18d817309f3","tid":1004549,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一定好撚後悔"},{"pid":"41b20b25337aff594bbefc1311c46ae142ee6c6f","tid":1004549,"uid":75050,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"934f8e582d0933a099400732b9b7e18d817309f3","tid":1004549,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一定好撚後悔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"點會後悔，嫁劉華同做單親老母無分別，唔係比人踢爆劉華根本無打算認結左婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84affaf55e4b3fed3c5074cede5d91219d47f12","tid":1004549,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"41b20b25337aff594bbefc1